author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Kitchen floor self-leveling tips…I cover all screws or nails with Feather Finish. Then add silicone and sill seal at the wall. Because I’m using Ardex K22F, I only need to prime the plywood. Horseshoe shims are my height indicators and make the pouring process a breeze 👍🏽🔥#selflevelling #kitchenremodel #remodeling
title: Kitchen Self-Leveling Tips - #shorts #homerepairtutor
